== -Operation "Festnahme" ==
<center>
'''Conducted by:''' XONE Containment Team 5

'''Mission Date:''' 14/07/2024

'''Location:''' [[Level Fun]]

'''Objective:''' Capture and contain the entity known as the ''Party Host'' or [[Caius Taggert|Sir Caius Taggert]].

==== Mission Log ====
'''09:42:'''

XONE Containment Team 5 entered [[Level Fun]] via noclip. Creepy laughter was detected across all frequencies. The local atmosphere carries high concentrations of aerosolized sugar compounds and synthetic helium, with a faint hint of hydrochloric acid. Heavy Scouts have been on a state of high alert. Researchers suggest a possible ambush nearby.

'''09:57:'''

Auditory anomalies increase. The XONE Team reports voices mimicking personnel names. No hostile actions observed yet from the enemy side, the XONE team proceeds with caution and down the hallway of [[Level Fun/The Party Rooms|level fun]].

'''10:05:'''

Visual contact with the '''[[Caius Taggert|Party Host]]''' has been established. The entity has greeted the personnel personally and asks if they want to become infected with the [[Sanguine Festivus]] casually; no sign of violence or hostile threat detected ''yet.''

'''10:13:'''

Type-6 Steel Net deployed. The subject exhibited no visible struggle, having called loudly for the other Partygoers. Analyzing reaction for signs of sudden movement. The subject laughed and asked the XONE team whether they would like to "join their ranks."

'''10:20:'''

Sanguine Festivus manifestations detected. Entities demonstrate heightened aggression and vocal synchronization with the Party Host’s speech patterns. Attempts to use AIFGs have failed. Scouts show the first sign of violent clashes.

'''10:18:'''

The battle ensues with many personnel dragged by the Sanguine Festivus into the corners of [[Level Fun]]. The retreat signal has been sent. Current contact with the XONE team has been severed; the XONE team has been classified as missing in action. 

'''10:20:'''

Agent Kraus transmits the mission aftermath debrief to the Chairman. Mission failed, 19 casualties, no conclusions drawn.

'''-End-'''


